					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-purple) mb-3">Remarkable Periodic Notes Generation</h3>
					<p class="text-(--color-text-muted) mb-4">Automatically generate daily, weekly, monthly, quarterly, and yearly notes directly in your Remarkable tablet with intelligent tagging for easy navigation. <span class="text-(--color-text-muted-dark) text-sm italic">(Coming Soon)</span></p>
